reviewText: I thought it was a cute movie for little kids.  Nothing great, but my granddaughter loved it.  She may want to watch it again, but it's not like the Disney or Pixar movies by any means.  It's just a cute cartoon movie.
Title: Bratz: Super Babyz

reviewText: My two little cousins could not get their eyes of this show. The valley girl personality of the characters were a bit much and what was up with the silky hair? But the show is for kids so I rated it accordingly.
summary: little cousins like it so I'm happy

reviewText: The Bratz get computer animated in this adventure film. After their sister accidentally gives the Bratz super powers, the girls must adapt to their new hero personalities. But as soon as they get used to the change, aliens return to earth and rob them of their powers.
